<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head> 
    <title> ToDo App </title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:100" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="/public/css/style.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet">

</head>

<body>
    <div class="jumbotron" style="background-color: #e8e8e8;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2 style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 5%"> Salient To Do List App </h2>

    <div class="row">
            <div class="form-group col">
                <h3 style="border-radius: 5px; position:relative; font-size:20px; font-weight:700;  letter-spacing:0px; text-transform:uppercase; width:250px; text-align:center; margin:auto; white-space:nowrap; border:2px solid #222;
                padding:5px 11px 3px 11px;padding-bottom: 3%;padding-top: 3%;">Add a new task</h3>
                <form action="/addtask" method="POST" style="padding-top: 10%;">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="newtask" name="newtask" placeholder="Add new task"> <br>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" id ="addbutton"> Add Task </button>
                </form>
            </div>

        <div class="col">
            
        <h3 style="border-radius: 5px; position:relative; font-size:20px; font-weight:700;  letter-spacing:0px; text-transform:uppercase; width:250px; text-align:center; margin:auto; white-space:nowrap; border:2px solid #222;
                padding:5px 11px 3px 11px;padding-bottom: 3%;padding-top: 3%; color:rgb(35, 27, 12); background-color:#fba404a4"> Pending Tasks </h3>

        <form class="form-group" action="/markcompleted" method="POST" style="padding-top: 10%;">
            <ul class="list-group" id="tasks>
                {{#each tasks}}
                    {{#unless this.Completed}}
                        <li class="list-group-item"">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="completedtasks" value="{{this.ID}}" id="task">
                            {{this.Task}}
                        </li>
                    {{/unless}}
                {{/each}}
            </ul>

            <button style="margin-top: 5%;" type="submit" class="btn btn-success"> Mark Completed </button>
        </form>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
            <h3 style="position:relative; font-size:20px; font-weight:700;  letter-spacing:0px; text-transform:uppercase; width:250px; text-align:center; margin:auto; white-space:nowrap; border:2px solid #222;border-radius:5px;
                padding:5px 11px 3px 11px;padding-bottom: 3%;padding-top: 3%;  color:rgb(35, 27, 12); background-color:#0af81a99"> Completed Tasks </h3>

            <ul class="list-group" style="padding-top: 10%;">
                {{#each tasks}}
                    {{#if this.Completed}}
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            {{this.Task}} 
                            <form action="/deletetask" method="post" style="display: inline;">
                                <input type="hidden" name="taskID" value="{{this.ID}}">
                                <button name="deleteTask" type="submit" id="deleteButton" style="float: right;" class="btn btn-danger">Delete</button>
                            </form>
                        </li>
                    {{/if}}
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
        </div>

</div>

       


       
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      
<style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap');

.container { 
    background-color: #e8e8e8;
  font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; 
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  max-width: 70%;
  padding: 28px;
  margin: 60px auto;
  border: 1px solid #eee;
  box-shadow: 0px 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
}

* { 
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  text-rendering: optimizelegibility;
  letter-spacing: -0.25px;
}

ol { padding-left: 50px; }
li { 
  color: #4F4F4F; 
  padding-left: 16px;
  margin-top: 24px;
  position: relative;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 20px;
  
  &:before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    height: 42px;
    width: 42px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid #ddd;
    position: absolute; // yeah, you have to manually position it based on the text size, line height, etc. (in the parent li style). it's not the smarest solution 
    top: -12px;
    left: -46px;
  }
}

strong { color: #292929; }

ol.alternating-colors { 
  li:nth-child(odd):before { border-color: #0BAD02; }
  li:nth-child(even):before { border-color: #2378D5; }
}
</style>
		<h1><u>Instructions for Using the Salient To-Do Web- Application</u></h1>

		<div class="instructions">
			<h2 style="font-size:large">Step 1:</h2>
			<ol>
				<li><p style="font: size 30px;">Open the to-do application in your web browser.</p> </li>
			</ol>

			<h2 style="font-size:large">Step 2:</h2>
			<ol>
				<li >Add a new task to the list by typing the task in the "Add new task" input field.</li>
				<li>Click the "Add Task" button to add the task to the list.</li>
			</ol>

			<h2 style="font-size:large">Step 3:</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>Mark a task as completed by clicking the checkbox next to the task in the "Pending Tasks" section.</li>
				<li>Click the "Mark Completed" button to mark the selected tasks as completed.</li>
			</ol>

			<h2 style="font-size:large">Step 4:</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>View completed tasks by navigating to the "Completed Tasks" section.</li>
				<li>Delete a completed task by clicking the "Delete" button next to the task.</li>
			</ol>

			<h2 style="font-size:large">Step 5:</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>To add another task, repeat steps 2-4.</li>
			</ol>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
